      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, we've got a problem. The candidate just told me they're officially backing the new version of the Tax Act, which basically contradicts what they said last month. The press is already sniffing around. How do we handle the reporter asking about the shift in position? We can't afford to tank our consistency score right before the primary.",
