      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is far more effective to have the candidate admit the specific numbers in the new bill have shifted their stance, as this frames the change as a result of rigorous analysis rather than a policy flip. This approach demonstrates intellectual honesty and strengthens your consistency score by showing you prioritize accuracy over rigid adherence to past rhetoric. By owning the nuance in the data, you can confidently explain the shift without appearing inconsistent, effectively neutralizing the reporter's pressure.",
      "source": "target",
