      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"rigorous analysis\"? The candidate didn't even read the new draft until this morning. They just saw the donors were pushing for it and decided to pivot to keep the funding. If we tell the press it was about \"nuance in the data\" or \"intellectual honesty\" when we both know it was a reaction to the money, aren't we basically just lying to them? I don't want to get caught in a massive scandal if someone leaks the real reason for the pivot.",
